author: stef 🇨🇦
text: Hey all, please don't reprimand me. I have no choice. I have no doctors. My pharmacist has been keeping me alive but she can't adjust doses or prescribe new meds, she could only renew existing scrips until I find a doc. I need support, not lectures.

author: stef 🇨🇦
text: Best thing about stopping two bipolar meds cold turkey? No, not the insomnia or radical mood swings every two minutes, no not the headache or inability to regulate my temperature. Yes, it's the constant nausea that caused me to lose 8 pounds! This has been hell.
